**Farmhand** | Solo Miscellaneous - Flock Team | Limited Transformation
__Basics__
The Farmhand wins with the shepherd and joins a channel with the shepherd to communicate securely.
__Details__
The Farmhand is usually the result of someone copying a member of the flock team for various reasons. This is because the shepherd and herding dog is too powerful for there to be two. 
